police bullets at the supermarket entrance.” Vanguard Four suspected robbers, said to be members of a gang that has been terrorizing Lagos and its environ for long, were yesterday killed during a shoot-out with operatives of the Special Anti-Robbery Squad, SARS, at the Airport Hotel axis of Awolowo Road, Ikeja, Lagos. August 8, 2014 In "News" UMUAHIA—ABIA State police command said yesterday that its men from Umuobiakwa police station in Obingwa Local Government Area of the state have arrested two armed robbery suspects and wounded four suspected kidnappers in a gun battle at Uratta Primary School in Isiala Ngwa North council. November 20, 2015 In "News" The police in Lagos on Thursday paraded four suspected armed robbers, including a pastor, whose gang specialises in attacking banks. February 13, 2014 In "News"